Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Located in the Heart of Fairfield

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to present for sale 36 Dale Street, Fairfield.

Situated on a commanding main road opposite Fairfield Railway Station, 36 Dale Street, Fairfield is a freestanding commercial building on a site area of 536sqm*. Mixed-use building in the heart of Fairfield!

36 Dale Street, Fairfield benefits from the following key attributes:
- B4: Mixed Use
- FSR: 2:1
- Offered with vacant possession
- Corner site
- Clear-span warehouse + well-presented office/showroom with extensive glass facades with maximum exposure & street appeal for business signage
- Full staff amenities
- Value add return on investment
- Development potential (STCA), circa ten (10) units + retail
- Located in Fairfield's thriving retail strip
- High pedestrian thoroughfare
- Walking distance to Fairfield Forum Shopping Centre
- Container access
- On-site parking x 6
- Close proximity to local amenities and public transport

For more information or to request access to the due diligence room, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

*Approximate

Note: All financial figures have been provided by the Vendor. Purchasers are advised to conduct their own independent due diligence.
